Synthetic population replication dataset

Source: R/db_replication_popl_tb.R
replication_popl_tb.Rd

A purely synthetic dataset, representative of the original study data, that can be used for replication runs of package algorithms.

Usage

replication_popl_tb

Format

An object of class tbl_df (inherits from tbl, data.frame) with 1711 rows and 43 columns.
